			<ul class="list-disc list--item-mb-xs  mb-4">
				<li>Always pay close attention to the ATM and your surroundings. Do your automated banking in a public, well-lit and clear location.</li>
				<li>Follow the instructions on the display screen, e.g. do not key in your PIN until the ATM requests you do so.</li>
				<li>Never force your card into the card slot.</li>
				<li>Do not allow people to look over your shoulder as you enter your PIN. </li>
				<li>Do not allow strangers to help you make transaction.</li>
				<li>Never use an ATM with a blank screen.</li>
				<li>If you see any suspicious devices in ATM area, do not use the machine. </li>
				<li>Take your card and receipt after the transaction.</li>
